大卫·吉尔莫表示新个人专辑是他自《月之暗面》以来制作的“最好”音乐https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-says-new-solo-album-is-the-best-music-hes-made-since-the-dark-side-of-the- Moon-3781177?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=david-gilmour-says-new-solo-album-is-the-best-music-hes-since-the-the-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-of-the-moonSurej Singh Tue, 06 Aug 2024 04:06:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3781177 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 2016 年现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《幸运与奇异》预计九月上映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-says-new-solo-album-is-the-best-music-hes-made-since-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-3781177">大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 表示，自《月之暗面》</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表以来，他制作的新个人专辑是“最好”的音乐。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 2016 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-gilmour">大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour)</a>谈到了他即将推出的个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-returns-with-luck-and-strange-his-first-new-solo-album-in-nine-years-3750328">《Luck And Strange》</a> ，他将这张专辑与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">平克·弗洛伊德 (Pink Floyd</a> ) 的《月之暗面》(Dark Side Of The Moon) 进行了比较 - 看看他在下面怎么说。</p><p>吉尔摩在开始个人职业生涯之前曾是平克·弗洛伊德乐队 (Pink Floyd) 的著名成员，他在接受<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/news/pink-floyd-legend-david-gilmour-is-on-the-cover-of-the-new-issue-of-prog-on-sale-now"><em>Prog 杂志</em></a>（通过<a href="https://www.guitarworld.com/news/david-gilmour-luck-and-strange-dark-side-of-the-moon-comparisons" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《吉他世界</em></a>》）采访时谈到他即将发行的唱片：“距《月之暗面》已经过去 50 多年了。我的感觉是这张专辑是自 1973 年《The Dark Side Of The Moon》问世以来我多年来制作的最好的专辑。”</p><p>这是高度赞扬，因为在《月之暗面》之后，平克·弗洛伊德继续发行了《动物》和《墙》等经典作品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752393" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752393" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752393" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024.jpg" alt="大卫·吉尔莫（Matthew Eisman/Getty Images 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752393" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·吉尔莫（Matthew Eisman/Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在与<em>Prog</em>的聊天中，吉尔莫开玩笑说他很快就会开始制作《Luck And Strange》的后续作品，并热切期待与专辑的几位合作者重聚：“我们的计划只是把这张专辑推出运行它，然后立即执行另一个。我将再次与所有这些人一起工作。”</p><p> 《幸运与奇异》定于 9 月 6 日发行，<a href="https://davidgilmour.lnk.to/LuckandStrange" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处预订/预保存</a>。这张密纹唱片在布莱顿和伦敦录制了五个多月。他的妻子、作家兼作词家波莉·桑普森 (Polly Sampson) <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">此前曾记录过吉尔莫参观工作室的经历，并</a><a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">在她的个人 Instagram 上分享了这些照片</a>。</p><p>曲目列表包括八首全新曲目以及 Montgolfier Brothers 1999 年曲目“Between Two Points”的改编版。到目前为止，这张专辑已经预演了两首单曲“The Piper&#39;s Call”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-david-gilmour-and-daughter-romanys-whimsical-new-single-between-two-points-3766354">蒙哥菲尔兄弟与他的女儿 Romany Gilmour 一起重新创作的 1999 年歌曲“Between Two Points”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750339" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750339" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750339" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn.jpg" alt="大卫·吉尔莫黑白新闻照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3750339" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·吉尔莫.图片来源：安东·科尔宾</figcaption></figure><div>吉尔莫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-announces-extra-shows-in-la-and-new-york-for-2024-3756979">今年将举办多场音乐会</a>，这是他八年来首次重返舞台。其中包括在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅举行的五场演出 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.[%E2%80%A6]tmaster.co.uk%2Fdavid-gilmour-tickets%2Fartist%2F769001" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买门票</a>。</div><div><h2><strong>大卫·吉尔莫 2024 年巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>27 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong><br /><strong>28 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong><br /><strong>29 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong></p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>1 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong><br /><strong>2 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong><br /><strong>3 – 意大利罗马，马西莫竞技场</strong><br /><strong>9 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>10 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>11 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>12 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>14 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>15 – 英国伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>29 – 加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，好莱坞露天剧场</strong><br /><strong>30 – 加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，好莱坞露天剧场<br />31 – 加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，好莱坞露天剧场</strong></p><p><strong>十一月</strong><br /><strong>4 – 纽约州纽约市麦迪逊广场花园</strong><br /><strong>5 – 纽约州纽约市麦迪逊广场花园<br />6 – 纽约，纽约州，麦迪逊广场花园<br />9 – 纽约，纽约州，麦迪逊广场花园</strong></p></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-says-new-solo-album-is-the-best-music-hes-made-since-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-3781177">大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 表示，自《月之暗面