8/bon-iver-kamala-harris@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/bon-iver-kamala-harris@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/bon-iver-kamala-harris@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">邦·艾弗 (Bon Iver)</a>已确认将在副总统<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris</a> ) 本周总统竞选活动的集会上表演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bon-iver-ii-album-review-2536398">Bon Iver – “我，我”评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/bon-iver-perform-kamala-harris-rally-wisconsin-1235746301/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>公告牌</em>报道</a>，卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 8 月 7 日在威斯康星州举行的集会将以 Bon Iver 为主角。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-vernon">贾斯汀·弗农</a>领导的乐队尚未公开表示支持哈里斯竞选总统，但鉴于他们已确认出席现任副总统即将举行的集会，因此推测他们将投票给现任副总统。 </p><figure id="attachment_3296228" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3296228" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3296228" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="Bon Iver 的贾斯汀·弗农。图片来源：C Brandon/Redferns via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Justin-Vernon-of-Bon-Iver.-Credit-C-BrandonRedferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3296228" class="wp-caption-text"> Bon Iver 的贾斯汀·弗农。图片来源：C Brandon/Redferns，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>卡马拉·哈里斯的团队<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/bon-iver-kamala-harris-wisconsin-rally-perform-1236096127/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在给<em>《综艺》杂志</em>的一份声明中</a>谈到了邦·艾弗的表现：“邦·艾弗正在参与其中，因为他们知道副总统哈里斯的价值观就是威斯康星州的价值观。主唱贾斯汀·弗农 (Justin Vernon) 将与乐队成员肖恩·凯里 (Sean Carey) 和迈克尔·刘易斯 (Michael Lewis) 一起庆祝他们两人称之为家乡的州，也是 Bon Iver 的创立地。”</p><p>声明继续说道：“Bon Iver 不断提升他们的家乡：他们不断在 Eaux Claires 音乐节上推出新音乐，并定期投资和提振当地经济。乐队还定期在威斯康星州举办 Get Out The Vote 活动。 2022 年，他们为威斯康星州发起了一项无党派努力，鼓励人们弥合分歧并参与政治进程——仅在过去一个月，他们就利用自己的平台提升了多个亲民主和民权组织的地位。” </p><figure id="attachment_3777450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="卡玛拉·哈里斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-widt